## Tips before your appliance repair visit in Srinagar

A little preparation helps diagnosis go faster and can reduce repeat visits:

- **Note brand, model, and approximate age** of the appliance when booking.
- **Describe symptoms clearly** — unusual sounds, error codes, leaks, or when the problem started.
- **Clear access** around the AC outdoor unit, fridge back, or washing machine connections.
- **Unplug the appliance** if you smell burning or see sparking, and mention this when you book.
- **Be home or have someone available** to show the unit and approve repair options.

If parts are needed, your technician can advise whether they carry common components or a follow-up visit is required after ordering. For AC servicing, booking before peak summer helps avoid long waits and keeps your home comfortable when temperatures rise.

